<h2>Application:</h2>
<p>

Wagging Tail is a non profit organization. It is run by volunteers located in Bangalore, India.
It is a website where people can adopt dogs which are rescued or give their pets up for adoption.
It is also a great opportunity for the people who are living in cities who can't afford to maintain a
dog, can come here and can adopt a dog for a day or two and experience joy.
This will encourage people to adopt rescued dogs and give them a home inturn will
drastically reduce the puppy mill crisis that is happening in recent times due to the increase in
adoption rate.<br>
All funds raised go directly towards rescuing and treating animals as well as awareness raising.
</p>
<h2>People who will use:</h2>
<ol>
    <li>People who have a dog and are willing to rent it to others to experience the joy of having
        a puppy when they have to go out of town for some work</li>
    <li>People who can't afford/manage a puppy rent(nursing) the puppy for a day or two and
        can experience the fun of having a pet.</li>
    <li>People who are interested can adopt the rescued pets or give their pets up for adoption.
    </li>
</ol>

